<section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-surface-container-lowest">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="text-xs font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-primary font-semibold">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="font-headline font-bold text-4xl text-on-surface mt-3">Shipping &amp; <span class="text-primary italic">Exchange Policy</span></h1>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mt-3">Last updated: April 2025</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-surface-container rounded-xl border border-surface-container-high p-8 space-y-8 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">1. Digital Products Only</h2>
        <p>All products sold by FullOnBaan — including eBooks (PDF format), video course bundles, and combo packages — are <strong class="text-on-surface">digital goods</strong>. No physical products are shipped. There is no physical delivery address required and no courier or postal shipping involved.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">2. Digital Delivery</h2>
        <p>Upon successful payment, your purchased materials are delivered electronically to the email address provided at checkout. Typical delivery time is within <strong class="text-on-surface">24 hours</strong> of confirmed payment. In most cases, delivery occurs within a few hours during business hours (9 AM – 8 PM IST).</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Please check your spam or junk folder if you do not see the delivery email in your inbox. If you have not received your materials within 24 hours, contact us at <a href="mailto:fullonbaan@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">fullonbaan@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">3. Delivery Requirements</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">To receive your digital products, you need:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li>A valid, active email address</li>
          <li>A device capable of opening PDF files (for eBooks)</li>
          <li>A stable internet connection (for video content)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">FullOnBaan is not responsible for non-delivery due to incorrect email addresses, full inboxes, or overly aggressive spam filters.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">4. Exchange Policy</h2>
        <p>Since all products are digital, traditional product exchange (swapping one item for another) is not applicable in most cases. However, if you have accidentally purchased the wrong product and have not yet received or accessed the materials, please contact us within <strong class="text-on-surface">2 hours</strong> of purchase, and we will make every effort to arrange an exchange of equivalent value.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Exchange requests are handled on a case-by-case basis and are subject to the discretion of FullOnBaan.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">5. Re-delivery Requests</h2>
        <p>If you did not receive your product due to a technical issue or an error on our part, we will re-deliver the content at no additional charge. To request re-delivery, email us at <a href="mailto:fullonbaan@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">fullonbaan@gmail.com</a> with your order reference and registered email address.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">6. No Physical Shipping Charges</h2>
        <p>As all our products are digital, there are no shipping charges. The amount charged at checkout includes only the product price and applicable GST (18%).</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">7. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any shipping or delivery concerns, please reach us at <a href="mailto:fullonbaan@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">fullonbaan@gmail.com</a> or call +91 63605 93122. You can also visit our <a href="/contact/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Contact page</a>.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
